ue over the term (aging-curve WAR walk x $4.71M/WAR, each year floored at the league minimum). Longer terms average in decline years, so the fair AAV falls. Real deals carry a term/security premium this does not model -- it is the production-fair anchor, not a prediction of the signing."}, "contractProjection": null, "contractAudit": null, "explain": {"scorecard": {"value": {"receipts": [{"label": "Even strength (5v5)", "value": "+2.62 WAR", "tone": "pos"}, {"label": "Special teams (PP + PK)", "value": "+0.53 WAR", "tone": "pos"}, {"label": "Penalty discipline (vs position)", "value": "-0.03 WAR", "tone": "neutral"}, {"label": "Faceoffs", "value": "-0.04 WAR", "tone": "neutral"}, {"label": "Total, last 3 seasons", "value": "+3.62 WAR", "tone": "pos", "strong": true}], "summary": "His total on-ice value, converted to WINS (WAR). It adds up everything he does \u2014 even-strength play, the power play and penalty kill, his penalty discipline RELATIVE TO HIS POSITION (defensemen structurally take more than they draw, so only the differential vs other D counts), and faceoffs \u2014 and the grade ranks that total against other players at his position over the last three seasons.", "method": "Total WAR sums these four, each priced in wins. The grade is this player's percentile vs same-position peers over the 3-season window."}, "overall": {"receipts": [{"label": "5v5 xG impact (RAPM)", "value": "+0.18 xG/60", "tone": "pos", "strong": true}, {"label": "\u2014 offense", "value": "+0.19 xG/60", "tone": "pos"}, {"label": "\u2014 defense", "value": "-0.01 xG/60", "tone": "neutral"}, {"label": "5v5 sample", "value": "3,262 min", "tone": "neutral"}, {"label": "On-ice xG share", "value": "48.3%", "tone": "neutral"}, {"label": "Relative to team (on \u2212 off ice)", "value": "-4.7%", "tone": "neg"}], "summary": "His two-way impact at 5-on-5: do his team's scoring chances go UP, and the other team's go DOWN, when he's on the ice? We isolate his effect from his linemates, the competi